Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was married by an imperial edit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a reasonable match that will last a hundred years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hopeless to be angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the pot calling the kettle black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have to say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Man marries, woman is married."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"King Xiang has dream, but Goddess is insensible"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone wants to be like Chief Qiao, who arbitrarily fills out the marriage contracts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thought I liked Mingyu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll tell you truthfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.83,0:07:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've also misunderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like 10th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But on Mingyu and 10th Prince's wedding night,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were obviously very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's difficult, then don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That night, I was very sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was because that day was the anniversary of my mother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the same day many years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Father has probably forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't like 10th brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why do you do so much for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like singing and folding paper cranes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know what Hong Funu was doing when Qiu Ranke first met her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hong Funu was brushing her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A relationship between a man and a woman could be like theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caring for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without romance and only sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good way to describe it. Without romance and only sincerity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Why don't we...\N-Go drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.53,0:08:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell us you were coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and tell Miss right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she can get rid of the man and come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.94,0:08:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.24,0:08:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toady I'm just here to drink with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just prepare some wine and dishes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll go prepare now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bosom buddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.83,0:09:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm bored,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come here to have a drink and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.10,0:09:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We would have a nice conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "ah", let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.99,0:09:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lady must be a courtesan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.11,0:09:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you prejudiced against her type?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everyone is equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.61,0:09:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince, Miss Luwu is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Death-Seeking 13th sister I've told you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I say, shouldn't we drink some?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the three of us talked from palace events
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.10,0:10:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to interesting stories of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the great north to Jiangnan in the south.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the poems to poets and wise men.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.76,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're also an admirer of Ji Kang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ji Kang's "Criticisms of the Famous Princes"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using your words,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he believes everyone has the ability to chase his/her own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One shouldn't be restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what your... Something... Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:10:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Self-determination?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is from the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.76,0:11:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One is a high-class lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't care about your wealth and status.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare to voice your opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.66,0:11:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is really admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot help yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also like us, wanting to live freely and unrestrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! I never thought that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would meet two bosom buddies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! For the three
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.66,0:11:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, -ancient people with modern ideas.\N -Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Here. \N -Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, 13th Prince, Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Greetings, 13th Prince, Second Miss. \N -Come
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.50,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go in by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, even though I returned late,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they won't make things difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better still go and tell 8th brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I returned late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruoxi, didn't you say that time was an exception, not a habit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see Jie'jie often looks at the man in the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless, Jie'jie knows him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.50,0:13:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He taught me horse riding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.03,0:13:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he is the person Jie'jie likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That year, Bei'le proposed to Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed the edict and married 8th Prince and became his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kneeled and begged Father, but the result was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I married 8th Prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was pregnant with his child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then wasn't everything over?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.89,0:14:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was 3 months pregnant,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.46,0:14:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that General died in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was depressed after I heard the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After a severe sickness, I also lost the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.26,0:14:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was 8th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sent someone to uncover about General.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Father sent him to be a frontline soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't kill Boren But Boren died because of me. (Chinese Idiom)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night, what happened with 13th Prince is ordinary in the modern times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the ancient times,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this ordinary happening is unacceptable to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already lost many things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose my ability to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though doing this will cause trouble for Jie'jie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think Jie'jie will help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found someone on the same wavelength at me in this time period.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I think about it, the happier I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to immediately go find him and go drinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, what are you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm drawing horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manga version.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.73,0:16:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master asked Second Miss to come to the study.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.06,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably about the drinking incident with 13th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.26,0:17:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, 8th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.06,0:17:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you go with 13th Prince yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince brought me somewhere to go drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.60,0:17:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really that scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Internal Bureau officer will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come. Eat a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that bangle come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rare Phoenix Blood Stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince treats you really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Among all the princes, 13th Prince stands out the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a heroic aura the others don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I still have to remind you that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With some things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, if you cannot make the decision, then don't ever think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.26,0:20:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiden selections.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man should set his sights afar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not wish for you to stay by my side forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.63,0:20:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the Shandong project.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the New Year. Let's not discuss this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.10,0:21:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.50,0:21:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Maiden selections are in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your family's Ruoxi is also entering, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Imperial Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That child is quite smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at the current situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.96,0:21:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruoxi's chance of being selected is very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her personality, living like that will be more painful than death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This triannual Maiden selection is how many girl's nightmare?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she catches His Majesty's eyes and becomes a concubine,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.03,0:21:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then she will be trapped in the palace for the rest of her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the Qing laws are considered fairly open,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.53,0:22:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the maidens only have to stay a few years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After they passed the age limit, they can be set free and get married as they wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a woman's most precious and youthful years are taken away like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.43,0:22:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch this happen to Ruoxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ruoxi is extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity she was born in this era, and with her background...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can we do to help her escape this fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.96,0:22:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least so that she doesn't become one of the Emperor's concubines.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this is a woman's destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.40,0:23:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.06,0:23:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bei'le is going to Ruolan's quarters to welcome the New Year?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.33,0:23:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But every New Year's Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you've always spent it here, welcoming the New Year with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.53,0:24:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I have prepared everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for Ruolan's side...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.93,0:24:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid it's cold and deserted all year round.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might not even have a New Year's scroll.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.53,0:24:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also afraid she won't serve you well
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.06,0:24:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and she won't be able to grant good fortune for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is prepared very well,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.76,0:24:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I already notified Ruolan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.36,0:24:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I would count down the New Year with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.10,0:24:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.56,0:24:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.60,0:24:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody is allowed to slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.36,0:24:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang the decorations well.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.40,0:24:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.50,0:25:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Eat a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.20,0:25:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Ruolan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.00,0:25:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Bei'le.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.46,0:25:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.26,0:25:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This New Year's Eve is so festive!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.00,0:25:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.13,0:25:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam hasn't been this happy in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Bei'le are both here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.26,0:25:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Qiaohui, we've walked for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.10,0:25:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's the meaning behind the sesame stalks?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.96,0:25:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is called "Stepping Age".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is auspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.46,0:25:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sesame stalks putting forth flowers notch by notch, higher and higher -- rising steadily.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.60,0:26:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jie'jie, it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.23,0:26:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go and see my bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.46,0:26:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look as if you haven't seen a bed for 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.73,0:26:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who told Second Miss to play so happily earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.70,0:26:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.90,0:26:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.36,0:26:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.93,0:26:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't sleep so early.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.86,0:26:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to greet the New Year today.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.60,0:26:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greet the New Year?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.50,0:26:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.50,0:26:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.26,0:26:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.30,0:26:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.30,0:26:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're sleepy, eat something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.10,0:26:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you eat, you won't be sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.36,0:26:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just ate a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.40,0:26:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to eat anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.20,0:26:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue playing a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.70,0:26:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and get some exercises by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.36,0:26:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.33,0:26:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't fall, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.06,0:26:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.26,0:27:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're sleepy, rest here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.83,0:27:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.70,0:27:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.90,0:27:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.60,0:27:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruolan, are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.70,0:27:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you take a rest too?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.49,0:27:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.66,0:27:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bei'le.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.06,0:27:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.10,0:27:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruoxi grew up in the barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.80,0:27:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She can't compare the city's princesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.06,0:27:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried that when she enters the palace, she'll cause trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.93,0:27:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I want to bother Bei'le,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.26,0:27:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you could tell the Momo and Anda (Head of Imperial Servants)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.93,0:28:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.30,0:28:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not considered a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.43,0:28:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you didn't ask, I would've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.63,0:28:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have something else you want to say, say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.83,0:28:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Ruoxi can avoid problem of the Maiden selection,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.96,0:28:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Father would arrange her marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.30,0:28:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think her relationship with 13th brother is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.13,0:28:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If 13th brother asks 4th brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.00,0:28:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then maybe, Crown Prince would help as a favor to 4th brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.30,0:28:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Bei'le can also help say something, then it might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.63,0:28:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to talk about the betrothal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.40,0:29:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.70,0:29:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let Ruoxi suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.70,0:29:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.70,0:29:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jie'jie usually treats 8th Prince coldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.16,0:29:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for me, she would gently ask him to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.90,0:29:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what exactly is 8th Prince thinking in his heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.16,0:29:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jie'jie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.16,0:29:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.36,0:29:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,New Year has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.56,0:29:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I've greeted the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.46,0:29:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.53,0:29:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-You stay here and slowly greet the New Year.\N-Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.76,0:29:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.60,0:29:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.53,0:29:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bei'le, it's already so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.00,0:29:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.43,0:29:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.03,0:29:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.33,0:29:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.53,0:29:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accomplish whatever I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.80,0:29:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.80,0:30:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.06,0:30:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss, don't sleep yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.76,0:30:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't washed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.13,0:30:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to sleep, I want to sleep...!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.76,0:30:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good that Madam greets the New Year every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.00,0:30:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she was like Miss and was only thinking about the bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.36,0:30:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who would ask for fortune for your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.36,0:30:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sleep too deeply, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.96,0:30:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get water for you to wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.10,0:31:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Children stayed awake on the night of the New Year's eve
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.10,0:31:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that parents can have long lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.43,0:31:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.73,0:31:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.73,0:31:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I miss you so very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.36,0:31:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I not miss you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.73,0:31:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.20,0:31:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I'll forget who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.16,0:31:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.76,0:31:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.26,0:31:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I Ruoxi or Zhang Xiao?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.00,0:32:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.26,0:32:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excused.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.50,0:32:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were fine earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.93,0:32:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it get like this on New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.46,0:32:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made a fool in front of 8th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.10,0:32:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just angry with myself for wanting to sleep and not being filial
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.80,0:32:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and forgot to pray for my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.86,0:32:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filial piety does not depend on these traditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.00,0:32:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is crying by yourself on New Year's considered filial?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.33,0:32:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you made an enormous mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.66,0:32:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to cause you to cry so badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.86,0:32:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel better after you've cried?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.76,0:32:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.73,0:33:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should return.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.00,0:33:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8th Prince, why aren't you staying the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.80,0:33:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sister is staying up on the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.50,0:33:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to prepare to enter the palace and greet Imperial Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.36,0:33:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to enter the palace this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.30,0:33:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that you cannot catch a quick nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.03,0:33:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then 8th Prince should rest and prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.10,0:33:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.13,0:33:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.66,0:34:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.16,0:34:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jie'jie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.46,0:34:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Jie'jie a happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.86,0:34:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering why you weren't here yet and you just came.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.63,0:34:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.73,0:34:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all Father and Mother's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.23,0:35:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They kept 10th Prince there and talked for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.46,0:35:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so anxiously watching them from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.46,0:35:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't want to ruin Mother's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.00,0:35:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year is the first time 10th Prince went to greet them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.20,0:35:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course Father and Mother would be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.60,0:35:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, they would talk for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.80,0:35:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold it against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.30,0:35:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A married daughter is like splashed water.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.80,0:35:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are already someone's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.90,0:35:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jie'jie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.93,0:35:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's 10th Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.23,0:35:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't he come with you to visit Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.33,0:35:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he still had work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.20,0:35:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I let him return first.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.16,0:35:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have 10th Prince by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.56,0:35:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last night I only had Hong Wang to greet the New Year with.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.20,0:35:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since dawn, I still haven't seen Bei'le yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.73,0:36:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the past, didn't Bei'le stay with Jie'jie to greet the New Year?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.36,0:36:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.00,0:36:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bei'le went to Ce'fujin's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.10,0:36:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the servants say.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.43,0:36:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was laughter throughout the entire night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.90,0:36:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bei'le only went back to his room at dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.73,0:36:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He changed his clothes and entered the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.56,0:36:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Bei'le is really...!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.46,0:36:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't stay with you and Hong Wang to greet the New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.80,0:36:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he go over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.66,0:36:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Ruoxi came, Bei'le took extra good care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.73,0:36:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every three to five days, he'll go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.30,0:36:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever there's something new, he sends it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.06,0:36:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Ruoxi is definitely not benevolent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.50,0:37:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's mature and could use tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.86,0:37:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the servants in the household and those princes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.50,0:37:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are all filled with praises for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.93,0:37:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.86,0:37:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, today, 10th Prince wanted to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.66,0:37:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw him like that, I knew he definitely wanted to find Ruoxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.96,0:37:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I hurried him back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.83,0:37:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maiden selections are coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.90,0:37:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope that after she leaves Bei'le's estate,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.33,0:37:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everything will return to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.13,0:37:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Jie'jie, the maiden selection...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.10,0:37:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.96,0:37:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.20,0:38:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, at the Mid-Autumn Festival, Imperial Father had a great impression of Ruoxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.06,0:38:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she catches Imperial Father's eyes this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.76,0:38:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then wouldn't she be even more arrogant?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.00,0:38:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, Bei'le.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.73,0:38:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, Bei'le.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.13,0:38:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.93,0:38:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.36,0:38:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's 10th brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.40,0:38:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he still had things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.73,0:38:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he returned first.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.30,0:38:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says a man will be more sensible after marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.10,0:38:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That seems to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.10,0:38:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bei'le is joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.76,0:38:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he have to do on New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.73,0:38:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After greeting the New Year last night, he was tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.83,0:38:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he wanted to return and sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.20,0:38:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he was afraid that you'll scold him.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.70,0:38:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he found a legitimate reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.30,0:39:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.33,0:39:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.06,0:39:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.16,0:39:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.46,0:39:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.53,0:39:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.10,0:39:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been unhappy for several days.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.80,0:39:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, there are so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.80,0:39:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.60,0:39:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second Miss, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.86,0:39:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how pretty that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.70,0:39:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.86,0:40:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So festive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.56,0:40:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.79,0:40:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.89,0:40:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.89,0:40:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not coincidental if you have the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.99,0:40:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This road leads to 8th brother's estate, it would be hard not to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.52,0:40:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how did you know I was coming out tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.66,0:40:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is such a great day,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.32,0:40:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you will just sit at home, wasting time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.46,0:40:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Qiaohui dragged me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.79,0:40:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.69,0:40:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, let's go take a look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.56,0:40:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.86,0:40:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invited Luwu out with us tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.02,0:40:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Luwu is coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.52,0:40:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great. The more the merrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.86,0:40:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? I didn't lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.12,0:40:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as the 13th Prince said.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.72,0:40:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Ruoxi is a genuinely carefree person.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.36,0:41:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Luwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.62,0:41:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're actually a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.99,0:41:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder "he" is so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.59,0:41:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I know that there's a great restaurant ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.96,0:41:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have some good food before we play the riddle game.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.92,0:41:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.76,0:41:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.12,0:41:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milord, we are crowded today.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.92,0:41:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've purposely arranged a quiet corner for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.96,0:41:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, we will have lion and dragon dance performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.76,0:41:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sit here, you can have a good view without finding your way through the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.69,0:41:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great. Get us some good food and wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.02,0:41:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.12,0:41:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Brother, you're here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.92,0:41:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings, 14th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.96,0:41:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.52,0:41:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise, there's no need for so much formalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.99,0:41:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We are on casual attire now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.29,0:41:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the rules. Have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.22,0:41:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Miss Luwu?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.22,0:41:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, everyone says Miss Luwu from the Capital is a very proud lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.96,0:42:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always find it strange. A high class courtesan is still a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.26,0:42:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she look down on money?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.56,0:42:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.22,0:42:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's 13th Prince's bosom buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.66,0:42:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A few months ago, I met Miss Luwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.56,0:42:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling still lingers in my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.99,0:42:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when I can visit you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.59,0:42:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If all of you weren't following the 14th Prince,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.69,0:42:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would have wondered which market you fishmongers were from.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.42,0:42:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare speak thus in front of the two princes?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.32,0:42:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.59,0:42:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're rather pretty as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.89,0:42:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps in future, your reputation will be higher than Miss Luwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.42,0:42:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Prince is indeed a Casanova.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.36,0:42:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has such good fortune with the ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.92,0:42:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-He's really-- \N-Cha Lin, Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.86,0:42:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and apologize. That's General Maertai's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.92,0:42:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know. Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.72,0:42:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.36,0:42:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruoxi should be getting home.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.19,0:43:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,13th Brother, I'll drink with you another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.39,0:43:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. I'll just have to trouble you to send her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.46,0:43:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't stand on ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.86,0:43:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my original intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.19,0:43:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.62,0:43:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.96,0:43:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luwu.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.62,0:43:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.26,0:43:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I was with the 13th Prince?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.46,0:43:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what if I was with a prostitute?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.09,0:43:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.42,0:43:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From everything you've seen in the Forbidden City,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.99,0:44:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,have you ever seen a lady of status associating with a girl from a brothel?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.16,0:44:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only know that the chaste lady, Luzhu, who died for love, was a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.36,0:44:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The heroine Liang Hongyu who protested against the barbarian invaders was also a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.32,0:44:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous Li Shishi who wouldn't submit to the barbarian invaders was also a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.92,0:44:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The woman who saved Emperor Heng, Lin Siniang was also a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.82,0:44:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady who dies for true love, Yuan Bao'er was also a prostitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.76,0:44:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, a prostitute can be a good person,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.76,0:44:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even become a person who deserves to be praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.72,0:44:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you tar all of them in one brushstroke?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.46,0:44:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,8th Brother, listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.49,0:44:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure knows how to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.16,0:44:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What rubbish has she been studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.29,0:44:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I study only concerns my father and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.82,0:44:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't any any right to meddle with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.46,0:44:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Stop arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.02,0:44:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,14th brother, why don't you head home first.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.56,0:44:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will handle this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.02,0:44:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A joke told by the Crown Prince is rather apt to this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.72,0:44:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you are not just like 13th brother in his fearless ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.02,0:45:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even his nonprejudicial ways
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.89,0:45:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and suave attitude is the same as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.79,0:45:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.82,0:45:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here and sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.89,0:45:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.39,0:45:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.22,0:45:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you scared about the Maiden selections?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.09,0:45:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The selections are almost here, but you still have the time to worry about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.26,0:45:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell if you're really scared or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.56,0:45:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Again with the selections.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.26,0:45:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is everyone mentioning it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.76,0:45:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.82,0:45:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hide or run from it. I can only sit and wait for it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.99,0:46:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I met your sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.32,0:46:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was only fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.56,0:46:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That year, your father came to the capital for work and she followed him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.49,0:46:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.79,0:46:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather was exceptionally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.46,0:46:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky was so blue, it looked as if it had been washed clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.30,0:46:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was a breeze that carried the fragrance of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.46,0:46:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was riding with two companions outside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.69,0:46:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the distance, I saw a young lady riding a horse on a hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.69,0:46:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have seen Ruolan's riding skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.99,0:46:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That day, she rode even better than she did in the fields today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.82,0:46:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her laughter was like silver bells ringing across the plains.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.75,0:46:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was full of joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.42,0:47:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who heard it felt happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.83,0:47:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't help but smile too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.91,0:47:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I couldn't believe what I was seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.81,0:47:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many beautiful ladies in the Forbidden City.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.89,0:47:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ruolan was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.16,0:47:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that time, my sister was in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.29,0:47:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She thought her love would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.10,0:47:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her happiness came from her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.94,0:47:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course she was different from the ladies in the Forbidden City who have never experienced love in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.80,0:47:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was the 8th Prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.70,0:47:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He sent men to investigate the general.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.50,0:47:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why father sent him to the frontline.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.47,0:47:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I returned home, I was busily trying to find out more about your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.29,0:47:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept thinking how I should request Imperial Father to gift her to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.59,0:47:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was trying to think of an idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.87,0:47:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imperial Mother told me
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.49,0:48:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Imperial Father wanted Maertai's eldest daughter to be my Ce'fujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.95,0:48:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, I realized I had never felt happier in my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.80,0:48:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day after Imperial Father made his decree,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.59,0:48:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I combed the entire city for a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.83,0:48:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I spent half a year before I found a phoenix-blood jade bangle
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.44,0:48:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to present to her on our wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.34,0:48:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the bangle?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.28,0:48:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The much-awaited wedding day finally arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.24,0:48:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I lifted the red veil,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.77,0:49:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that the situation wasn't what I imagined it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.70,0:49:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman that made me pine for her for two years
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.98,0:49:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the woman before me were two completely different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.65,0:49:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She never rode.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.05,0:49:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And she seldom smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.50,0:49:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I keep asking myself where I went wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.01,0:49:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I mistake her for someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.02,0:49:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I sent people to Xibei to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.14,0:49:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After much sleuthing, I finally found the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.60,0:49:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did that person die?
